    "The rhetorical situation is a useful tool to evaluate whether the content meets our goals.",
    "The next sections will throw light on what the rhetorical situation is, and ways in which it can be used for prompt engineering.",
    "A rhetorical approach to technical communication is intentional or purposeful (Smith 2008).",
